                      "name": "OrgMateBackgroundPictureOptionsUser",
                      "displayName": "Background image display method",
                      "explainText": "Sets the display method for the image specified by the Desktop Background Picture setting.\n\nPossible values:\n\n\"None\" (no);\n\n\"Wallpaper\" (mosaic) — duplicates the image in its original size so that the image completely covers the desktop;\n\n\"Centered\" — displays the image in the center of the desktop in accordance with the original image size;\n\n\"Scaled\" — enlarges the image, maintaining proportions, until the size of one of the image boundaries coincides with the size of one of the screen boundaries;\n\n\"Stretched\" — enlarges the image to fit the size of the desktop, changing the proportions if necessary;\n\n\"Zoom\" (scale) — enlarges the smallest side of the image until its value coincides with the size of the corresponding screen border; the image can be cropped on the other side;\n\n\"Spanned\" (fill) — enlarges the image, maintaining proportions, until the size of one of the image borders coincides with the size of one of the screen borders.\n\nThe \"Block\" option — (available only for machine policy) prevents the user from changing this setting. Blocking a policy makes it a priority over a similar policy for the user.",
